name: Discreet Cactus
description:
It is a dynamic and discreet cactus. Of course it's also responsible, decisive and energetic, but they're tainted by and mixed with habits of being malicious as well.
Its dynamic nature though, this is what it's often adored for. Others tend to count on this and its sociable nature whenever they need assistance or help.
Its discretion is there to relift spirits when needed.
